extends layout 

block content 

    body 

        if authorized == true 
            if isCompany == true
                ul 
                    li 
                        a(class="active" href="/users/index" class="glyphicon glyphicon-user") Profile
                    li 
                        a(href="/users/offers") Offers 
                    li 
                        a(href="/users/jobRequests") Job request   

                form(method='post' action='/users/addOffer') 
                    p
                        label 
                            | Name
                        input(id="user_name" type='text' name='title' placeholder="Title of offer", required)
                    p
                        label 
                            | Description
                        textarea(type='text' name='description' placeholder="Description of offer", required)
                    p 
                        label
                            | Phone 
                        input(type='text' name="phone" placeholder="Enter your number", required)   

                    br    
                    button(type="submit" class='button') Enter your data         

            else if isCompany == false     
                ul 
                    li 
                        a(class="active" href="/users/index" class="glyphicon glyphicon-user") Profile
                    li 
                        a(href="/users/offers") Offers 
                h1(class='mainH1') Our top offers for You!
                div(class='divOffers') 
                    a(href="/users/walkingDogs")  
                        img(src="../images/close-up-traveler-walking-with-dog.jpg" width="350" height="280")
                        div(class='text-block')
                            p Walking dogs 
                        div(class='Description')
                            p Dog owners enjoy numerous health and social benefits by walking their dog a few times a week. Benefits include improved cardiovascular fitness, lower blood pressure, stronger muscles and bones (built up by walking regularly), and decreased stress.
                            p A regular walk is vitally important for your pet's health too. Obesity in pets is associated with a number of medical complaints including osteoarthritis, cardiovascular disease, liver disease and insulin resistance...    
                            p Most dogs need to be walked at least once each day, though some dogs, particularly very active dogs, may require more. The breed of dog you have, as well as its level of fitness and age, will also determine how long and how vigorous your walk should be...            
                br        
                div(class='divOffers')
                    a(href="/users/babysitter")
                        img(src="../images/pexels-alex-green-5691820.jpg" width='350' height='280')
                        div(class='text-block')
                            p Babysitting  
                        div(class='Description')
                            p Learning to set limits and boundaries for the children, as well as how to make decisions on the spot when the children don't automatically follow these limits and boundaries.
                            p Gaining independency at a time when they may feel like they have little control at home.
                            p Acquiring Increased empathy towards others and the ability to see something from a different perspective...

        else            
            ul 
                li 
                    a(class="active" href="/users/index" class="glyphicon glyphicon-user") Profile 
                li 
                    a( href="/users/socialMedia") Login  
                li
                    a(href='/users/register') Register
            br    
            div(class ='fading')
                h1(class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft" style='font-size:60px;color:white;margin-left:480px;font-weight:800') Welcome to our website!
                img(src='../images/gettyimages-1210530753-2048x2048.jpg' width='340' height='290' class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft")
                img(src='../images/gettyimages-811911828-2048x2048.jpg' width='340' height='290' class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft")
                img(src='../images/happy-family-paying-their-groceries.jpg' width='340' height='290' class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft")
                img(src='../images/education-concept-student-studying-brainstorming-campus-concept-close-up-students-discussing-their-subject-books-textbooks-selective-focus.jpg' width='340' height='290' class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft")
            br
            div(class="hero-image")
                div(class="hero-text")
                    h1(style="font-size:50px") Find the job that will fit you
                    p You can see our offers here 
                    br
                    a(href="/users/offers" class="button" role="button" data-bs-toggle="button") Offers
        








